## Rules

- Any `eval()`, `Function()`, `exec()` with user-influenced data is Critical, no exceptions.
- Template engines: user data must ONLY be variables, NEVER part of the template source.
- SSRF: DNS resolution must happen before IP validation — hostname allowlists alone are bypassable.
- Always check for second-order injection. The vulnerable sink may be in completely different code from the input handler.
